{"tid":504431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老公捉姦】美女教師搭上學生 受害人父收告密電郵","createTime":"2017-12-20T03:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T15:45:00.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f37775ff0e7f804019abccfb0bea360b73087d7a","tid":504431,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"美國俄勒岡州一名女教師色誘校內一名未成年男生，與他多次發生性關係，月初終被自己的丈夫捉姦在床。其後男學生的父親收到告密電郵，女教師上周五在家中被捕。<br />\n<br />\n29歲的巴伯（Andrea Baber）本月5日與男學生在家中偷情，被自己的丈夫捉姦在床。男生的父親上周收到匿名電郵，其中更附有多張巴伯與男生在床上的親熱照片，揭發巴伯與其兒子的姦情。<br />\n<br />\n警方指兩人去年開始關係，當時男生只有15歲，之後兩人「定期」約會，巴伯更向男生供應大麻。她被控強姦及非法向18歲以下人士提供大麻。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"d0d2599a2faa10f2e01704568d5217f93fbaa2ac","tid":504431,"uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.oregonlive.com/home/olive-media/width600/img/pacific-northwest-news/photo/andrea-baberjpg-2213c648b97b5fc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.oregonlive.com%2Fhome%2Folive-media%2Fwidth600%2Fimg%2Fpacific-northwest-news%2Fphoto%2Fandrea-baberjpg-2213c648b97b5fc2.jpg&h=7c182bc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f27f8d5324e25fab50c21f66b415970f42eae05","tid":504431,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"乜撚都無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae142c8fed301947e4a383fbe3ec94899220d1ff","tid":504431,"uid":5253,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"真係喪盡天良 細路仔都搞<br />\n要搞就搞樓主呀嘛"},{"pid":"f7400c6f11c092c881d4c709e44ec64ee8ee239a","tid":504431,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"咁正都話冇講過？"},{"pid":"496d8e307a32f51994f6700604726778137dfdad","tid":504431,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"我係個老豆都睇唔過眼啦"},{"pid":"0f133825eff3483f727109e7655d